title: Dave Bautista Pt. 1

description:
For a total badass, former WWE star Dave Bautista (Guardians of the Galaxy, Spectre, Blade Runner) sure is a nice guy. In this week’s two-part episode, Anna and Sim meet up with Dave in Atlanta, on location for Guardians of the Galaxy: Vol 2. Dave shares his remarkable journey from the streets of San Francisco, to the WWE ring, to the set of a blockbuster franchise—with a few stints in jail along the way! The gang also discusses life on the set of GOTG2, Dave’s all-time favorite workout playlist, and the wonder that is Japanese toilets. Later, they play a new WWE-inspired game, in which Dave must match famous wrestlers with their catch-phrases. 

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
